OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFirms told to pay out over 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fforced meter fittings      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy firms should start compensating 
OL,6, customers whose homes were wrongfully  
OL,7, fitted with a prepayment meter, without
OL,8, waiting for the results of a major     
OL,9, review, the regulator has said.        
OL,11,FOfgem chief executive Jonathan Brearley
OL,12,Fsaid companies must review their own   
OL,13,Fmeter installations immediately.       
OL,15,FA six-week pause in forced prepayment  
OL,16,Ffittings lasts until the end of March. 
OL,18,FIt came after debt agents for British  
OL,19,FGas broke into vulnerable people's     
OL,20,Fhomes to force-fit meters.             
